input.sentences: last week i ordered some parts for my computer .
the box arrived all banged up with the instructions on top .
the fan that came with the box was cracked .
i had to repack everything and send it back .
output.sentences: Finally my part arrived to fix my computer!
Figures! The directions are in Chinese.
Let's see if I can figure out how to replace these parts.
My motherboard is completely fried thanks to a broken fan.
Luckily my computer was under warranty so I can send these broken parts back to the manufacturer.
